snippet.title: Farewell North - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
In the latest trailer for Farewell North, developer Kyle Banks walks you through a segment of the open-world adventure game. Farewell North stars a dog and its human owner, as you guide her through puzzles, all while restoring color to the world around you.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
